<subSubSection pageId="5" pageNumber="124" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,694,1079]" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,874,899]" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">Remarks.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName box="[324,477,874,899]" class="Insecta" family="Argidae" genus="Arge" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="deckerti">
<emphasis box="[324,477,874,899]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">Arge deckerti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is very similar to 
<taxonomicName authority="Kohl, 1893" authorityName="Kohl" authorityYear="1893" box="[691,1007,874,899]" class="Insecta" family="Argidae" genus="Arge" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stuhlmanni">
<emphasis box="[691,849,874,899]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">A. stuhlmanni</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Kohl" box="[866,999,874,899]" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" refString="Kohl, F. F. (1893) Hymenopteren von Herrn Dr. Fr. Stuhlmann in Ostafrika gesammelt. Jahrbuch der Hamburgischen Wissenschaftlichen Anstalten, 10 (2), 179 - 191." type="journal article" year="1893">
Kohl, 
<number box="[940,999,875,899]" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" value="1893.0">1893</number>
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
, both being widely distributed (
<bibRefCitation author="Koch" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" refString="Koch, F. (2005) The sawflies of the BIOTA - Southern Africa Project with description of new species of Arge (Insecta, Hymenoptera, Symphyta). Mitteilungen aus dem Museum fur Naturkunde in Berlin, Zoologische Reihe, 81 (2), 193 - 199. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnz. 200510012" type="journal article" year="2005">
Koch 
<number box="[151,211,910,935]" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" value="2005.0">2005</number>
</bibRefCitation>
), but 
<taxonomicName box="[273,394,910,935]" class="Insecta" family="Argidae" genus="Arge" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="deckerti">
<emphasis box="[273,394,910,935]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">A. deckerti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
clearly differs by the entirely yellow costa of the fore wing. In 
<taxonomicName box="[1105,1261,910,935]" class="Insecta" family="Argidae" genus="Arge" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stuhlmanni">
<emphasis box="[1105,1261,910,935]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">A. stuhlmanni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
the colouration of the costa and subcosta varies from a black apical half to blackish at extreme apex adjacent to the stigma. The lancet of 
<taxonomicName box="[260,383,982,1007]" class="Insecta" family="Argidae" genus="Arge" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="deckerti">
<emphasis box="[260,383,982,1007]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">A. deckerti</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is uniformly covered with sensilla, which are absent in 
<taxonomicName box="[1035,1193,982,1007]" class="Insecta" family="Argidae" genus="Arge" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stuhlmanni">
<emphasis box="[1035,1193,982,1007]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">A. stuhlmanni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and the serrulae are flatter. In lateral view, the penis valve of 
<taxonomicName box="[612,768,1018,1043]" class="Insecta" family="Argidae" genus="Arge" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stuhlmanni">
<emphasis box="[612,768,1018,1043]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">A. stuhlmanni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is distinctly broader than in 
<taxonomicName authority="Koch 2005" authorityName="Koch" authorityYear="2005" box="[1092,1367,1018,1043]" class="Insecta" family="Argidae" genus="Arge" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="deckerti">
<emphasis box="[1092,1213,1018,1043]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">A. deckerti</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Koch" box="[1229,1360,1018,1043]" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" refString="Koch, F. (2005) The sawflies of the BIOTA - Southern Africa Project with description of new species of Arge (Insecta, Hymenoptera, Symphyta). Mitteilungen aus dem Museum fur Naturkunde in Berlin, Zoologische Reihe, 81 (2), 193 - 199. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1002 / mmnz. 200510012" type="journal article" year="2005">
Koch 
<number box="[1299,1360,1018,1043]" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" value="2005.0">2005</number>
</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
. Until now 
<taxonomicName box="[206,361,1054,1079]" class="Insecta" family="Argidae" genus="Arge" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="124" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="stuhlmanni">
<emphasis box="[206,361,1054,1079]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">A. stuhlmanni</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is not reported for 
<collectingCountry box="[577,676,1054,1079]" name="Ethiopia" pageId="5" pageNumber="124">Ethiopia</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
